.TH tftp 3 "tftp 1.2.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
tftp \- Trivial FTP.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Interface module for the \fItftp\fR application.

.SS "Overwiew"

.PP
This is a complete implementation of the following IETF standards:


.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
RFC 1350, The TFTP Protocol (revision 2).

.RE

.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
