.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
\fB\fI{max_tsize, MaxTsize::pos_integer() | infinity}\fR\fR

.PP
Threshold for the maximal filesize in bytes. The transfer is aborted if the limit is exceeded. Default is \fIinfinity\fR.

.RE


.sp
